OL,4,G2200FAlbert Finney: Talking Pictures
OL,5,     GA retrospective look at
OL,6,     Gtelevision appearances made over
OL,7,     Gthe years by award-winning actor
OL,8,     GAlbert Finney, with archive
OL,9,     Ginterviews and classic clips.
OL,10,     GNarrated by Sylvia Syms.
OL,11,G2235FThe Importance of Being Earnest
OL,12,     GReese Witherspoon stars as the
OL,13,     Gobject of affection for two men
OL,14,     Gusing the same alias.
OL,15,G0005FThe Secret Life of the Sun
OL,16,     GKate Humble and Helen Czerski
OL,17,     Greveal the inner workings of the
OL,18,     Gsun and investigate why
OL,19,     Gscientists think changes in the
OL,20,     Gsun's behaviour may have powerful
OL,21,     Geffects on our climate.
